COG Weaponsmith 
Age: 225 yrs 
Race: Gnome 
Class: Artificer 
Rank: Fellow 

![Cortix Gearcreque.png](data:image/png;base64,)

Cortix is an inventor! He loves anything magical and making it better. He crafts the regular weapons most members are in need of easily with his machines but loves to research and find new ways to help his fellow members get the best gear around. If you hear an explosion, it's probably Cortix, though he doesn't seem to mind them, unlike Darrum. The Weapon forge and the Armory are next to each other for obvious reasons and the two who run them despise each other. There has been a long rivalry between them for as long as anyone can remember, though no one really knows why it continues. They are set to one up each other at any moment and some may say they like to argue but both will deny it and say they wish the other will fall off a cliff.
